/#
   The physical delivery conditions for coal.
 #/
record FpML5.transparency.CoalDelivery {
  # The point at which the Coal Product will be delivered and received.
  deliveryPoint : string

  # The point at which the Coal Product as a reference to the Source of the Coal Product. This should be a reference to the source element within product.
  deliveryAtSource : boolean

  # Specifies how the risk associated with the delivery is assigned.
  risk : string?

}

deliveryPoint.Doc: The point at which the Coal Product will be delivered and received.
deliveryPoint.Name: deliveryPoint

deliveryAtSource.Doc: The point at which the Coal Product as a reference to the Source of the Coal Product. This should be a reference to the source element within product.
deliveryAtSource.Name: deliveryAtSource

risk.Doc: Specifies how the risk associated with the delivery is assigned.
risk.Name: risk
